Example of a CRUD grid using ExtJS, Spring Framework 3 and Hibernate 3.5.

All libs included.

First of all execute the MySQL scrip: sql/script.sql

I used Eclipse Helios and Tomcat 7.0 to develop this app. 
This project is in Eclipse dynamic web project format.

Download this example and run it in a java app server.
http://localhost:8080/extjs-crud-grid-spring-hibernate/

GPL 3.0 license included.

For more examples and tutorials:
http://loianegroner.com (English)
http://loiane.com (Portuguese - BR)